    Jean-Christophe> Yes,  there  is one  by  Claude Marché,  available  (in  a very  first
    Jean-Christophe> release) at:

    Jean-Christophe> 	 http://www.lri.fr/~marche/tmp/regexp-0.1.tar.gz

